snTrapFIPSSharedSecretZeroized TRAP-TYPE	 
 	ENTERPRISE foundry
   VARIABLES { snAgGblTrapMessage }
   DESCRIPTION
                   "The SNMP trap that is generated when shared secret are zeroized in FIPS mode"
